query:
SELECT 
    v.id as 'ID Venda',
    DATE_FORMAT(v.dataVenda, '%d/%m/%Y') as 'Data Venda',
    COALESCE(t.codigo, '-') as 'Código Turma',
    COALESCE(f.nome, '-') as 'Nome Formando',
    v.valorTotal / 100 as 'Valor Bruto (R$)',
    v.valorLiquido / 100 as 'Valor Líquido (R$)',
    v.status as 'Status',
    v.excluido as 'Excluído',
    u.name as 'Criado Por',
    DATE_FORMAT(v.createdAt, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%i:%s') as 'Data Criação'
FROM vendas v 
LEFT JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id 
LEFT JOIN turmas t ON f.turmaId = t.id
LEFT JOIN users u ON v.createdBy = u.id
WHERE YEAR(v.dataVenda) = 2026
  AND MONTH(v.dataVenda) = 6
  AND DAY(v.dataVenda) = 15
ORDER BY v.id
